    "causal_summary": "There is no convergence-gated loop that assembles implementation-ready context from the existing codebase. `/speckit:plan` discovers context ad-hoc (4 one-shot exploration agents in Step 5) and `/speckit:implement` relies on whatever the plan captured, so reusable code is missed (violating the \"reuse, avoid new code\" principle), context-rot and stale references creep in, and there is no saturation signal for \"enough context gathered.\"",
